  "body": "Hi all,\r\n\r\nThis is a tracking issue to implement the block operations as defined in the current spec [here](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/master/specs/core/0_beacon-chain.md#per-epoch-processing). \r\n\r\nThis can be split into separate PRs implementing each section including:\r\n- helper functions:\r\n- calculate `total_balance` of all the validators\r\n- calculate `base_reward_quotient` and `base_reward` of each validator\r\n- justify the epoch boundary block\r\n- justify the epoch boundary block at the start of the previous epoch\r\n- update receipt roots\r\n- update justification\r\n- update finalization\r\n",
